    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This jagged, bony growth narrows to a sharp, pointed tip. Deep groves from some former battle scar its surface. The bearer of a *saurian spike* often feels a sudden surge in power and confidence. The spell attack modifier of any spell cast by activating this item is +15.\n* **Armor** You gain imprecise scent with a range of 30 feet.\n* **Weapon** (auditory, emotion, fear, visual) When you cast a polymorph spell by activating the spike, your battle form is exceptionally fearsome. Each enemy in a 30-foot emanation must succeed at a DC 27 Will saving throw or become frightened 1 (frightened 2 on a critical failure).",
        "level": 9,
        "traits": [
            {
